'''Lionnel Mpasi Nzau''' (born 1 August 1994) is a professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for {{French football updater|Le Havre}} club [[Le Havre AC|Le Havre]]. Born in France, he plays for the [[DR Congo national football team|DR Congo national team]].

== Early life ==
Mpasi was born in [[Meaux]], in the eastern suburbs of Paris, to [[Democratic Republic of the Congo|Congolese]] parents.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Muko |date=2021-01-20 |title=Lionel Mpasi-Nzau (Rodez): "Représenter la patrie ? Ce serait un grand plaisir !" |url=https://www.leopardsfoot.com/lionel-mpasi-nzau-rodez-representer-la-patrie-ce-serait-un-grand-plaisir/ |access-date=2024-01-07 |website=LEOPARDSFOOT |language=fr-FR}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=September 17, 2019 |title=Les Échos de Muko: Bolasie démarre fort, Bakagoal frappe pour la reprise, Mpoku décisif |url=https://www.leopardsfoot.com/les-echos-de-muko-bolasie-demarre-fort-bakagoal-frappe-pour-la-reprise-mpoku-decisif/}}</ref> He acquired [[French nationality law|French nationality]] on 31 August 2000, through the collective effect of his father's [[naturalization]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=JORF n° 0203 du 2 septembre 2000 – Légifrance |url=https://www.legifrance.gouv.fr/jorf/jo/2000/09/02/0203 |access-date=2024-01-07 |website=legifrance.gouv.fr}}</ref>

==Club career==
A youth product of [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|PSG]], Mpasi signed his first professional contract with [[Toulouse FC|Toulouse]] before moving to [[Rodez AF|Rodez]] in 2016.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lesviolets.com/actu/mpasi-redecouvrir-le-stadium-avec-rodez-c-est-juste-incroyable-,50218.html|title=Mpasi: "Redécouvrir le Stadium avec Rodez, c'est juste incroyable"|website=LesViolets.Com}}</ref> Mpasi made his professional debut with Rodez in a 0–0 [[Ligue 2]] tie with [[Le Mans FC]] on 14 February 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ca.soccerway.com/matches/2020/02/14/france/ligue-2/le-mans-union-club-72/rodez-aveyron-football/3031257/|title=Le Mans vs. Rodez – 14 February 2020 – Soccerway|website=ca.soccerway.com}}</ref>

On 13 July 2025, Mpasi signed a two-season contract with [[Le Havre AC|Le Havre]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Le Havre AC|url=https://www.hac-foot.com/actualite/lionel-mpasi-rejoint-le-hac.html|title=Lionel Mpasi rejoint le HAC !|trans-title=Lionel Mpasi joins HAC!|date=13 July 2025|access-date=1 August 2025|language=fr}}</ref>

==International career==
Mpasi is a former youth international for France.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.footpy.fr/Coupe-de-France-Lionel-MPASI-Rodez-Je-me-mets-en-mode-competition_a10297.html|title=Coupe de France – Lionel MPASI (Rodez): " Je me mets en mode compétition "|first=Fabien|last=Calabresi|website=www.footpy.fr|access-date=23 February 2020|archive-date=23 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223055720/https://www.footpy.fr/Coupe-de-France-Lionel-MPASI-Rodez-Je-me-mets-en-mode-competition_a10297.html|url-status=dead}}</ref> However, he decided to represent the home country of his parents, DR Congo. Being selected without appearing on the pitch, he finally debuted for the [[DR Congo national football team|DR Congo national team]] in a 1–0 friendly loss to [[Bahrain national football team|Bahrain]] on 1 February 2022.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newsofbahrain.com/sports/78432.html|title=Bahrain beat DR Congo in friendly &#124; THE DAILY TRIBUNE &#124; KINGDOM OF BAHRAIN|website=DT News}}</ref>

On 27 December 2023, he was selected from the list of 24 Congolese players selected by [[Sébastien Desabre]] to participate in the [[2023 Africa Cup of Nations]]. As a full goalkeeper, he contested the three first-round matches, all ended in a tie against [[Zambia national football team|Zambia]] 1–1 and [[Morocco national football team|Morocco]] 1–1 and [[Tanzania national football team|Tanzania]] 0–0, respectively. In the eighth final, against the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt]] team, he scored the last shot at the goal, with the game ending in a 1–1 draw.<ref>https://twitter.com/MickyJnr__/status/1751756873378791774</ref>

